General.Name: Farstarcap Investment Corp
General.Description: Farstarcap Investment Corp. does not have significant operations. The company intends to identify, evaluate, and acquire assets, properties, and businesses, which would constitute a qualifying transaction. The company was formerly known as Mobile Mining Technologies Inc. and changed its name to Farstarcap Investment Corp. in September 2017. Farstarcap Investment Corp. was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
